Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.85,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.31,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Jotaro! L-Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.98,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Be careful, Koichi! Don't get any closer to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:13.24,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you to look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.33,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Is that his Stand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.67,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:32.80,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-He's here! He's trying to take the jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.34,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.55,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I can't believe he chose {\i1}now{\i0} to pick up his suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.02,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That jacket is important evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.64,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.60,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't make any hasty decisions without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.36,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Something about this Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.07,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...seems really dangerous!
Comment: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:00.03,Main,,0,0,0,,OPENING
Comment: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.28,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,643)\pos(142,900)\fs60}Episode 23: {\fs80} Sheer Heart Attack Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.25,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,A bomb... It's a bomb Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:33.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Is this how he got Shigechi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.01,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,No wonder we couldn't find his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.14,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-H-He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.18,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't pursue him, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.81,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't pursue him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.31,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:53.73,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,If we catch him,\N we'll know for sure who killed Reimi and Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:59.11,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We need to act carefully and deliberately, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.37,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:06.33,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Not seeing the name tag inside the jacket was unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:11.08,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,However, just from looking at the jacket, \Nwe can infer that this guy is about 175 centimeters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.17,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He's unmarried and works an office job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.01,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If he had a wife, he wouldn't have brought his jacket here for a simple button repair. {sexist af}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:24.26,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He's somewhere around twenty-five to \Nthirty-five years old, and wealthy to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:28.64,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Judging by the material and design,\N his jacket is a designer brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:33.40,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Even if we let him go, we've significantly \Nlowered the number of potential culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.15,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.28,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,W-Wait! That doesn't mean we shouldn't go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.90,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,He's a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.95,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't want to, but we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That bomb Stand is still hiding somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.95,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?! His Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.87,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.01,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I didn't, but it has to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:03.01,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We need to carefully exit through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It has to be? Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,How can you say that for sure\N when you can't even see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.39,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If he were the kind of guy that would leave \Nright after killing the store owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:17.02,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...there's no way he would have gotten away \Nwith his crimes for the last fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.40,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He'll get rid of any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.53,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,In effect, he'll get rid of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:28.03,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... \NDon't you think you're being a bit paranoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:34.17,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,If his Stand isn't here, \Nthen the serial killer and his jacket must be long gone by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.42,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Listen up, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:40.92,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Observation doesn't mean looking around, it means looking around {\i1}carefully{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.93,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,To not just listen, but to listen {\i1}well{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.59,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.93,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...we're as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:56.44,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-He's acting like he knows everything, \Nbut my Echoes isn't useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:02.19,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Jotaro underestimating me \Neven though I've grown so much stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:06.36,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Do you really think that bomb Stand \Nis still somewhere around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,We're gonna look pretty dumb if it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.58,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.08,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-It really was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.12,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,If I don't get it off me, it's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.54,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.09,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:29.85,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.27,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It took all my punches... This thing is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.44,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.82,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Star Platinum: The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:52.33,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I hate drawn-out battles, so let's finish this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.16,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:07.30,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.30,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.14,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-You did it! You must have stopped time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.14,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Now we can touch it all we want, and it won't explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:30.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Those who search for I, Kira Yoshikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.83,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...will perish in an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:39.96,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My Stand, Killer Queen's Sheer Heart Attack, \Nalways eliminates its targets without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.80,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,N-No way! Star Platinum's power wasn't enough to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.35,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,A-A Stand that's this tough... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.10,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Stand back, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.44,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.19,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.37,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's still coming for us! It hasn't even slowed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Get back, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.71,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Even though you've hurt yourself from attacking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.00,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...it still hasn't been damaged at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.84,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You need to get farther back, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.13,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.13,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Oww, oww, oww, oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.80,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.81,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It will explode if you keep touching it! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.18,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.08,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:02.96,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break. I've never encountered such a sturdy Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.25,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,My resolve is gonna break before this thing does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:10.38,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Jotaro, we're gonna get \Nblown to bits if we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.13,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You need to get farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.39,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'll rip it apart for sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.43,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,L-Listen to me for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.52,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,If a Stand is controlled from far away, it can't move with that much power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.89,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,So if you consider the power behind\N that thing's explosive attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:28.11,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's no way that kind of power \Nis possible unless the user is nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:32.15,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,The user has to be at most fifteen... \NNo, ten meters from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.70,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.12,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}And?! {\i0}It's only ten meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,My Echoes has a fifty meter range!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.87,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It can find the serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.79,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I already told you, Koichi. Don't go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:48.38,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Right now you need to be able to protect yourself with Echoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.00,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't send it away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.88,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.88,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,The killer is long gone from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.09,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,His Stand is remotely controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:00.77,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I've been through enough Stand encounters \Nto know it when I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.39,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.90,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Its actions are too simple to be the result of direct control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.90,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,You know it when you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.82,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:13.07,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's no way such a powerful Stand \Ncould be controlled remotely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.32,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,The user is definitely close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.78,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro isn't taking me seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.83,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I've grown a lot stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.91,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I can find the killer and defeat him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.13,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Distance, ten meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.51,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Th-There he is! It's him!\N He's holding the jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.64,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,But this doesn't make any sense... H-He's too far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.06,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,He's more than fifty meters away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.98,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,And he's getting farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.06,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,He's outside of Echoes' range!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.15,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-His bomb Stand is being controlled remotely?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.03,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.90,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,That much power working from so far away makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.04,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.29,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What? It's coming for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.29,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:16.17,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,His Stand chooses its target \Nby attacking where it senses the most heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.14,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That's why it's so powerful, \Ndespite its user being so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.93,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Call out Echoes and protect yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.35,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Even if I stop time, you're too far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.81,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,O-Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.31,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Echoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.57,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...is still fifty meters away near the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.32,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.32,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:40.41,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Star Platinum: The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.50,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:55.21,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That thing attacked the store owner first \Nsince he was holding a hot drink in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:59.55,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Then it targeted Koichi since his body temperature rose after he started getting worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.35,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If it senses something hotter, it should target that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.60,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Resume time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.73,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:15.82,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It targets whatever is giving off the most heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.57,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:22.95,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But come to think of it, if the heat from a person's body is enough to set it off, then being near a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.83,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.83,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro!
Comment: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.57,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,How could this happen?\N This is all my fault, Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's all because I went after the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.87,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,If you hadn't stopped time and started the fire to protect me, it wouldn't have gotten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wake up, Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:20.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro! Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:25.84,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,That explosion was not set off by a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.31,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.36,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's trying to finish us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.82,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.12,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's just like Mr. Jotaro said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:56.54,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It will attack anything giving off \Nmore heat than a human body first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.54,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Now's my chance to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.80,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I need to call Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,He can heal Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.55,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I have to call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.19,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,This is... the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's loads of heat sources in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I need to buy some time so we can escape through the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.44,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:30.66,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute... This isn't a gas stove!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.20,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Why did this house have to have an electric stove?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's gonna take too long to warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.21,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,The oven is electric, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.38,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.71,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I know! This should have some hot water in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.72,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Target {\i1}this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.26,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.20,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:17.04,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wait... Now that I'm observing carefully like Mr. Jotaro said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...I know what this thing's weakness is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,A weakness I didn't think of earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:36.64,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Why should I have to be a coward and \Nrun away in fear while asking God to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.52,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It should be the other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:47.24,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,And why the hell should I be the one who feels like they'd rather be searching for a public restroom with a bad case of the runs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.66,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.91,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,If anyone should be running away in fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.83,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...it's you, you serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:15:00.37,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's been attacking the hottest targets this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.71,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...but that's exactly what its biggest weakness is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:08.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Being relentless is its biggest weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.68,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's been almost three minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:18.35,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on at that shoe store...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.94,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...but there's one thing I know to be truer \Nthan anything else in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.82,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Sheer Heart Attack has no weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.45,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It will track down its targets, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:36.33,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,With that taken care of, now I can finally call Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.70,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hopefully he's home right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.71,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,SFX: Sizzle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.72,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's lost track of us for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:56.72,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Have fun chasing that sizzling sound effect around forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:01.48,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's just like a donkey chasing a carrot \Ndangling in front of its face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.56,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That's your biggest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.61,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hello, Higashikata residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:09.53,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Josuke, it's Koichi! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.82,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro is hurt bad, and it's all my fault! \NJust hurry and get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.87,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,What did you say?! You can't just drop that on me! \NI don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.50,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and get over here! We finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.21,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,We found the serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I captured his Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.63,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You captured {\i1}what{\i0} now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, I still don't understand! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:40.89,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's hot! I turned it off, but it keeps getting hotter and hotter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.73,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,What's with this piece of junk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.15,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to cook with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:49.15,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Koichi! You gotta tell me where you are right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.53,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.70,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Damn! It's ignoring the sound effect and coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.16,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}Koichi, where are you? Hurry up and tell me, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm at Centipede Shoes! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:09.17,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Damn! The sound effect on Echoes' tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.30,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It got destroyed in the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.68,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.43,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,That explosion was not set off by a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.39,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.11,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-It's coming! It's coming after me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.77,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,But I can't use the tail's sound effect anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.36,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.40,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,How can I fight it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.62,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Echoes Act 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,What's going on? Echoes Act 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Act 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.01,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Where are you, Act 2?! \NWhy won't you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.81,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Act 2! It was killed in the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.98,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It split in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.69,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,N-No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:17.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,If the explosion had killed it, \NI would have died along with it since I'm its user!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:22.99,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I remember now! \NThere was another time Echoes looked like it had died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.24,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-It...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,C-Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.05,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Echoes Act 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.97,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Umm, do you want me to call you {\i1}sir?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.48,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,What is your command?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:50.19,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,D-Does this mean I've grown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.11,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,My Act 3 is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.44,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,What is your command?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:01.62,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what you can do yet, s-so for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.62,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Protect us, Act 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:12.50,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Umm, will you protect us, please? \NYou can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.42,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.42,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,This wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.06,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-My Stand is so fast now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.98,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's even faster than Act 1 and Act 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:44.16,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,Finishing Blow: Echoes 3 Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.13,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Act 3?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.09,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,This enemy is strong. My punches were ineffective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ineffective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:06.14,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,The enemy possesses a very heavy power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.10,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,S-H-I-T!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.85,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,I was outmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.81,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Outmatched? Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.86,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I told you to protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.65,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,I have succeeded in protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.36,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,Just as I was commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.61,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.99,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You succeeded?! In what way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:30.12,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You're completely useless! \NI haven't grown at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.38,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over he{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.68,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This is taking too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Why is Sheer Heart Attack taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:59.44,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on? My left hand just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My hand that released Sheer Heart Attack suddenly feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:10.20,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Good sir, is something the matter? Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.33,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine. I'll pay for the broken cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.71,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm leaving, so could you get me the check?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,M-My left hand... is so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.64,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,S-Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! My left hand! My left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.23,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,It feels like someone attached a heavy weight to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:35.52,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.60,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Are you okay, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.15,Secondary,Kira,0,0,0,,D-Don't mind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.15,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Please, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.32,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:45.07,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,What are you doing, sir? How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.03,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It sank into the pavement and can barely move...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:53.33,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Act 3! What did you do? This power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.91,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,3 Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.33,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,I just combined three and freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:01.42,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Act 3, what kind of power is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Why is it moving so slowly? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:09.59,Main,Echoes,0,0,0,,I simply afflicted it in way beyond your comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:12.10,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,My hand feels so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:17.06,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Sheer Heart Attack somehow became incredibly heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.90,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,This is bad. I need to get it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:23.69,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I need to get Sheer Heart Attack back at all costs!
