Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.81,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HFAF2ED&}Something important is being taken from me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.23,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HFAF2ED&}By a demon that's thrust itself into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:27.60,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC4B3D4&}Everything is crumbling around me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.40,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}Living my life as if everything was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.78,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}Until suddenly it was stolen away without warning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:36.24,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}This is my only chance to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:40.58,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Those who fight with a heart pierced by the arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.08,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Are a beautiful sight to behold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.12,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Anywhere you go I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.75,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}Anywhere you go I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.88,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}I'll always chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.04,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}I will chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.63,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}You can't escape me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:55.30,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Run faster as I chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.43,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Even tomorrow I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.30,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Until I finally pummel you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:05.93,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&&HEEF7F1&&}My perseverance will propel me forward to achieve victory
